Country endings
men of the country: -ας/-ος
women: -δα


Greek last names: male vs female
If the last name ends in:
-ις -> η
-ος -> ου
-ας -> α



μου του ....　can be used as personal pronouns. but they go before the word. μου αρέσει

adjectives
end with -ος -η/α -ο



